  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "All I need do to make the evidence point to Jim Pike is say, \"A great xtian + Freedom fighter came back from the dead (1) + took me over + imposed his personality + habits onto mine.\" + like, \"He drove a different car + was well-to-do.\" + to nail it down: \"He revealed that the civil rights leaders had been murdered by conspirators, + the murdered included Jim Pike,\" +, \"He put some biblical material in my novel + esp a dream about an innocent man being murdered.\"\n\n(1) i.e I found myself \"on the ",
      "matched_alias": "Elisha",
      "term_id": "TERM_elisha",
      "term_name": "Elisha",
      "term_slug": "elisha"
    },
    {
      "text": "Last edit over 5 years ago by sekennedy62\n74\nComplete\n74\n543-9389 Messiah\n\nThis is not a normal response to believing something (which is not true, obviously); + so I conclude that what I believed is is. + all I had to do to experience it all was believe so it was really always (already) there - all the time. ➀\n\n[Diagram]",
      "matched_alias": "Messiah",
      "term_id": "TERM_messiah",
      "term_name": "Messiah",
      "term_slug": "messiah"
    }
  ],
